  "title": "InstantSearch.js v2",
  "body": "This PR contains the changes for the V2 of InstantSearch.js.\r\n\r\nThis new version brings:\r\n - connectors API, and with it the capability of reusing the logic of the widgets without their rendering\r\n - better documentation, with more in-depth description of the different aspects of the library, a getting started and guides\r\n - some clean up in the API",
